Name: Rank
Description: The rank value of the dimension for which the selection criteria apply.

Name: AllValues
Description: If set to "true" applies to the full set of dimension values. If set to "false" use specificValue, rangeMinimum and rangeMaximum as appropriate to define the subset of values needed.

Name: SpecificValue
Description: May contain a single value or a delimited array of values.

Name: RangeMinimum
Description: The inclusive minimum value of the range. Use when the values or subset of values are ordered and contiguous and may be expressed as a range.

Name: RangeMaximum
Description: The inclusive maximum value of the range. Use when the values or subset of values are ordered and contiguous and may be expressed as a range.
